# No Git Commit or Push

NEVER execute `git commit` or `git push` commands. Instead:

1. Stage files with `git add` as normal
2. Print the proposed commit message and description directly in the chat
3. Let the user commit and push manually

This applies to all situations, even when the user asks you to "create a commit" or "commit the changes".
